_model: blog-post
---
title: Welcome!
---
body:

Hi, I am Thabang, and this is my <a href="/about/">website</a> I am an Industrial Engineer based in Johannesburg, South Africa.

> "Abandon all hope, ye who enter here."
> — Dante Alighieri

For the Curious, this website was built using a custom [Distill](https://distill.pub/guide/) - 
[Tufte](https://edwardtufte.github.io/tufte-css/) stylsheet and [Lektor](https://www.getlektor.com/). 
The fonts used are [Source Serif 4](https://fonts.google.com/specimen/Source+Serif+4) and [Source Sans 3](https://fonts.google.com/specimen/Source+Sans+3).